Previous studies have shown that PPV is affected by many factors. However, the type of explosive, explosive density, and rock mass characteristics are similar in actual blasting. A project often requires repeated blasting in the same area. Considering the influence of the burden, PPV in a coal mine can be expressed as:1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
