				\begin{document}$$VAF = \left( {1 - \frac{{{\text{var}} \left( {x_{m} - x_{p} } \right)}}{{{\text{var}} \left( {x_{m} } \right)}}} \right)*100$$\end{document}31\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
